<p begin="0t" end="13140000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle0">Processed by 繁化姬 dict-2fa2bf69-r1017 @ 2023/01/22 23:05:26 | https://zhconvert.org</p>
<p begin="13140000t" end="39040000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle1">我们查不到你的前妻美春小姐</p>
<p begin="39060000t" end="89930000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle2">在晚上7点半从花店下班后的行踪</p>
<p begin="96960000t" end="137460000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle3">发现遗体的河岸应该就是凶杀现场</p>
<p begin="144670000t" end="158750000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle4">尽管还不清楚过程</p>
<p begin="158750000t" end="180440000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle5">但她的头部遭受钝器反复殴打</p>
<p begin="180450000t" end="203790000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle6">手上也留有防御造成的伤痕</p>
<p begin="208970000t" end="225890000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle7">可以推测她一开始被从身后殴打</p>
<p begin="225910000t" end="265100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle8">接着转身反抗犯人才遭到杀害</p>
<p begin="269680000t" end="290540000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle9">由于犯人没有抢夺她身上的财物</p>
<p begin="290560000t" end="313060000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle10">我们认为犯人的动机是出于仇恨</p>
<p begin="337830000t" end="365210000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle11">目前还没找到凶器</p>
<p begin="365210000t" end="378950000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle12">这是9月12日</p>
<p begin="378960000t" end="395240000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle13">周六晚间发生的事情</p>
<p begin="395240000t" end="422770000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle14">我和美春离婚超过一年了</p>
<p begin="422770000t" end="451120000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle15">期间完全没见过面也没有联络</p>
<p begin="451130000t" end="469900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle16">不管是她在花店工作</p>
<p begin="469900000t" end="485700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle17">还是住在隔壁县</p>
<p begin="485700000t" end="501180000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle18">我都是第一次听说</p>
<p begin="501180000t" end="522030000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle19">另外关于两位离婚的理由</p>
<p begin="522040000t" end="556220000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle20">你对外宣称是因为美春小姐外遇</p>
<p begin="556240000t" end="594600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle21">但实际上是因为她想谋杀你吧</p>
<p begin="594620000t" end="607100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle22">你们怎么会知道</p>
<p begin="702960000t" end="726320000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle23">在四季中转瞬即逝之冬</p>
<p begin="726320000t" end="754680000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle24">有位如雪般的美人</p>
<p begin="754680000t" end="777210000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle25">折羽织缎只为祈愿</p>
<p begin="777210000t" end="805570000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle26">落下泪珠化身为鹤</p>
<p begin="805570000t" end="828080000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle27">踏上寻找世界尽头旅途</p>
<p begin="828080000t" end="856440000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle28">沙漠中的少年</p>
<p begin="856440000t" end="878970000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle29">释放了神灯的精灵</p>
<p begin="878970000t" end="907330000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle30">获得无可取代的财富</p>
<p begin="907330000t" end="959470000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle31">精巧隐瞒的真象 形同幻化</p>
<p begin="959470000t" end="993670000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle32">之中能有什么意义?</p>
<p begin="993670000t" end="1033290000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle33">人生! 一切! 皆是! 神秘!</p>
<p begin="1048730000t" end="1092930000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle34">让我们背对太阳</p>
<p begin="1092930000t" end="1146740000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle35">轻轻为无形的未来染上色彩</p>
<p begin="1146740000t" end="1195130000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle36">来杯刚泡好热腾腾的红茶吧</p>
<p begin="1195130000t" end="1223900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle37">宴会已经开始了</p>
<p begin="1223900000t" end="1258110000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle38">快告诉我 夜色中的故事</p>
<p begin="1281790000t" end="1301560000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle39">那是去年3月发生的事</p>
<p begin="1301570000t" end="1317820000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle40">我要开车去上班时</p>
<p begin="1317830000t" end="1351180000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle41">平时喝的营养补给饮品里被混入了安眠药</p>
<p begin="1358540000t" end="1369550000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle42">路上小心</p>
<p begin="1369550000t" end="1379550000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle43">谢谢</p>
<p begin="1411170000t" end="1421690000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle44">是</p>
<p begin="1421690000t" end="1443780000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle45">我边讲电话边走出家门</p>
<p begin="1443790000t" end="1482990000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle46">顺手把瓶子放进口袋里就开车走了</p>
<p begin="1490970000t" end="1512600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle47">电话是客户打来的</p>
<p begin="1512620000t" end="1545970000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle48">我为了拿资料先绕去公司一趟</p>
<p begin="1608520000t" end="1637720000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle49">多亏接连的巧合我才得以幸存</p>
<p begin="1644910000t" end="1685690000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle50">我认为妻子是最有可能混入安眠药的人</p>
<p begin="1693190000t" end="1722810000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle51">请人调查之后 才知道原来她有外遇</p>
<p begin="1728780000t" end="1742830000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle52">我给她看了调查结果</p>
<p begin="1742840000t" end="1762000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle53">她便承认杀人未遂的罪</p>
<p begin="1770920000t" end="1785800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle54">照她原本的计划</p>
<p begin="1785800000t" end="1816390000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle55">安眠药应该会在我上高速公路后生效</p>
<p begin="1823970000t" end="1866090000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle56">听说目的是获得我的遗产后跟情夫结婚</p>
<p begin="1872010000t" end="1906740000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle57">但是为什么警察会知道这件事?</p>
<p begin="1911620000t" end="1933850000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle58">我没有告诉过任何人</p>
<p begin="1933870000t" end="1968890000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle59">美春也说过她是瞒着情夫犯案的</p>
<p begin="1968890000t" end="1981400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle60">在那之前</p>
<p begin="1981410000t" end="2005180000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle61">请你先说明为什么没有告前妻</p>
<p begin="2023770000t" end="2058560000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle62">杀人未遂判不了多重的刑</p>
<p begin="2069200000t" end="2084430000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle63">这么说来你在学生时代</p>
<p begin="2084430000t" end="2107770000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle64">也差点被朋友杀害过呢</p>
<p begin="2107780000t" end="2137810000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle65">是的 所以我知道告她也没有用</p>
<p begin="2154170000t" end="2177840000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle66">好歹是相爱才结婚的妻子</p>
<p begin="2177860000t" end="2206160000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle67">也幸好我本人并没有受伤</p>
<p begin="2211340000t" end="2223310000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle68">老顾着工作</p>
<p begin="2223320000t" end="2265020000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle69">让她寂寞到去找别人的我也有不对</p>
<p begin="2265020000t" end="2289200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle70">然而她外遇是事实</p>
<p begin="2289210000t" end="2317160000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle71">你也握有杀人未遂的证据</p>
<p begin="2317170000t" end="2339670000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle72">离婚时无论你开什么条件</p>
<p begin="2339680000t" end="2359260000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle73">美春小姐都只能答应吧</p>
<p begin="2365250000t" end="2397340000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle74">但你却仍公平地将财产分给她</p>
<p begin="2403060000t" end="2421000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle75">毕竟是法律保障的权利</p>
<p begin="2421020000t" end="2436030000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle76">要是做得太绝</p>
<p begin="2436040000t" end="2456870000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle77">反过来让她更恨我也很困扰</p>
<p begin="2456880000t" end="2477740000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle78">的确是有那种可能性</p>
<p begin="2477750000t" end="2529440000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle79">她离婚后似乎马上被情夫提分手</p>
<p begin="2529440000t" end="2554900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle80">那笔赡养费在经济面上确实帮助不小吧</p>
<p begin="2554910000t" end="2586320000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle81">或许你跟外貌不同 人挺温柔的</p>
<p begin="2591750000t" end="2618700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle82">然而美春小姐并没有接受你的好意呢</p>
<p begin="2632590000t" end="2657400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle83">美春小姐在家里藏了一封写着</p>
<p begin="2657400000t" end="2687690000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle84">"如果我离奇死亡 一定是遭他杀害"</p>
<p begin="2687690000t" end="2722500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle85">"请立刻逮捕他"的告发信</p>
<p begin="2726960000t" end="2773020000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle86">信中也写了意图谋杀你导致离婚的过程</p>
<p begin="2778430000t" end="2795140000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle87">若非如此</p>
<p begin="2795140000t" end="2836840000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle88">我们也不会知道你们之间的内情</p>
<p begin="2848220000t" end="2866870000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle89">不管她写了什么</p>
<p begin="2866870000t" end="2893570000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle90">我都没有理由要杀她吧</p>
<p begin="2893580000t" end="2944870000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle91">美春小姐似乎非常恐惧被你报复哦</p>
<p begin="2944870000t" end="2979900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle92">她本来意图杀害你获得所有财产</p>
<p begin="2979900000t" end="2997420000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle93">所以被你怨恨也是理所当然的</p>
<p begin="2997420000t" end="3023270000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle94">但你却没有报警</p>
<p begin="3023290000t" end="3037450000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle95">只提出了离婚</p>
<p begin="3037470000t" end="3055810000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle96">甚至连财产也分给她</p>
<p begin="3055810000t" end="3097930000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle97">还对周遭隐瞒真相保住她的颜面</p>
<p begin="3097950000t" end="3118790000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle98">心胸宽广也该有个限度</p>
<p begin="3118790000t" end="3146750000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle99">这些作为对她来说反而更可怕</p>
<p begin="3157780000t" end="3187610000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle100">的确是好到恶心的滥好人呢…</p>
<p begin="3187590000t" end="3208790000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle101">所以她怀疑你这么做是不是</p>
<p begin="3208790000t" end="3239300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle102">用来掩饰之后要杀死她的烟雾弹</p>
<p begin="3245790000t" end="3263920000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle103">你一定是为了在她遭到杀害时</p>
<p begin="3263940000t" end="3288550000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle104">不让警方怀疑到你头上</p>
<p begin="3288550000t" end="3315240000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle105">才会刻意装出和平离婚的样子</p>
<p begin="3315240000t" end="3337350000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle106">美春小姐是这么写的</p>
<p begin="3337350000t" end="3375720000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle107">所以你才不跟周围提起杀人未遂的事</p>
<p begin="3375720000t" end="3405740000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle108">还总是说自己也有错</p>
<p begin="3405760000t" end="3424080000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle109">猜忌也该有个限度</p>
<p begin="3428620000t" end="3472900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle110">我才没卑鄙到要花这些时间心力报复她</p>
<p begin="3472900000t" end="3490830000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle111">要是真有那种力气</p>
<p begin="3490840000t" end="3512930000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle112">我又怎么会躲在这种地方</p>
<p begin="3523090000t" end="3557140000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle113">算了 现在反驳什么都没用</p>
<p begin="3557160000t" end="3585090000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle114">学生时代想谋杀你的那位朋友</p>
<p begin="3585090000t" end="3609270000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle115">也已经过世了呢</p>
<p begin="3609280000t" end="3640550000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle116">是在山中杀人未遂事件的3年后吧</p>
<p begin="3640570000t" end="3654320000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle117">纪录是写交通意外</p>
<p begin="3654320000t" end="3668920000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle118">好像是吧</p>
<p begin="3668940000t" end="3693940000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle119">我也只是听说 并不清楚详情</p>
<p begin="3693960000t" end="3723140000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle120">那件事我们姑且做了确认</p>
<p begin="3723140000t" end="3749830000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle121">没找到跟你有关的线索</p>
<p begin="3749850000t" end="3764850000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle122">也没有人怀疑你</p>
<p begin="3764870000t" end="3776530000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle123">那是当然的</p>
<p begin="3776530000t" end="3812810000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle124">但美春小姐知道后认为是你做的</p>
<p begin="3812830000t" end="3838670000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle125">使她对自身的危机感变得更强烈了</p>
<p begin="3838690000t" end="3868290000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle126">她坚信自己也一样会遭受你的报复</p>
<p begin="3868290000t" end="3905830000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle127">所以才不惜写明自己罪状也要留下这封信</p>
<p begin="3905840000t" end="3927520000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle128">警方竟然相信这种东西吗</p>
<p begin="3927520000t" end="3952950000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle129">其实美春小姐遗体的掌心</p>
<p begin="3952970000t" end="3980050000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle130">有用签字笔写了文字</p>
<p begin="3990930000t" end="4012180000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle131">她死的时候手是握紧的</p>
<p begin="4012200000t" end="4031370000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle132">所以犯人也没发现吧</p>
<p begin="4037470000t" end="4062230000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle133">她写的时候似乎很慌张没有看着手心</p>
<p begin="4067540000t" end="4098940000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle134">随身物品中并没有找到签字笔</p>
<p begin="4098940000t" end="4135620000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle135">也许是为了不让犯人发现偷偷丢掉了</p>
<p begin="4140650000t" end="4159800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle136">她手心里写了</p>
<p begin="4159820000t" end="4189440000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle137">能以片假名念作"MASAYU"的字</p>
<p begin="4189460000t" end="4215290000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle138">你的名字是MASAYUKI对吧</p>
<p begin="4227710000t" end="4250330000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle139">可能是写到一半差点被发现</p>
<p begin="4250350000t" end="4267010000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle140">就只写了这样</p>
<p begin="4267020000t" end="4279540000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle141">如果只写到一半的话</p>
<p begin="4279540000t" end="4304540000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle142">下一个字也不一定是KI吧</p>
<p begin="4317470000t" end="4329590000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle143">的确</p>
<p begin="4329590000t" end="4362110000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle144">也可能本来是想写KO却写成YU</p>
<p begin="4374080000t" end="4384220000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle145">话说回来</p>
<p begin="4384230000t" end="4412590000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle146">9月12日晚间八点到十点之间</p>
<p begin="4412590000t" end="4430930000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle147">你人在哪里呢</p>
<p begin="4440450000t" end="4468050000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle148">9月12日…</p>
<p begin="4481890000t" end="4491820000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle149">请看这个</p>
<p begin="4500760000t" end="4541050000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle150">这是离这里最近的购物中心的监视器影像</p>
<p begin="4541050000t" end="4558530000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle151">日期是9月4日</p>
<p begin="4558550000t" end="4578580000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle152">是事件发生的8天前</p>
<p begin="4578500000t" end="4622300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle153">上面照到一位很像是美春小姐的女性跟你走在一起</p>
<p begin="4639390000t" end="4678700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle154">你刚才说你们离婚后从来没见过面…</p>
<p begin="4687900000t" end="4705380000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle155">她只是很像美春</p>
<p begin="4705380000t" end="4720810000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle156">不是同一个人</p>
<p begin="4720810000t" end="4742490000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle157">那么这位小姐又是哪里的谁呢</p>
<p begin="4794700000t" end="4828820000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle158">麻烦你跟我们到附近的警察局一趟吧</p>
<p begin="4908750000t" end="4935170000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle159">要先回山上吗</p>
<p begin="4935190000t" end="4963550000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle160">不 还是在这等呢…</p>
<p begin="5115570000t" end="5124950000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle161">美…</p>
<p begin="5185810000t" end="5201290000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle162">回来得真晚啊</p>
<p begin="5206140000t" end="5232980000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle163">人都死了还给你添麻烦</p>
<p begin="5232990000t" end="5253010000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle164">那女人可真过分呢</p>
<p begin="5253020000t" end="5273450000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle165">不过你也得反省反省</p>
<p begin="5273460000t" end="5293460000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle166">要是有跟邻居打好关系</p>
<p begin="5293470000t" end="5321820000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle167">说不定就会有那个叫不在场证明的东西啦</p>
<p begin="5321830000t" end="5334750000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle168">你说得没错</p>
<p begin="5334760000t" end="5350190000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle169">不过也不是没有不在场证明</p>
<p begin="5370720000t" end="5396490000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle170">9月12日晚上八点那时</p>
<p begin="5396490000t" end="5421520000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle171">我正好在跟你吃天妇罗</p>
<p begin="5436470000t" end="5466970000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle172">那天我们享用天妇罗和好酒直到深夜</p>
<p begin="5466970000t" end="5485320000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle173">我隔天早上才回去的</p>
<p begin="5485330000t" end="5510340000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle174">那犯人就不可能是你啊</p>
<p begin="5510350000t" end="5527580000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle175">这下不就解决了吗</p>
<p begin="5532350000t" end="5577910000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle176">但是我又不可能跟警察说证人是雪女</p>
<p begin="5587600000t" end="5602930000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle177">要是被问到不在场证明时</p>
<p begin="5602940000t" end="5629210000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle178">我马上回答没有的话就好了</p>
<p begin="5634410000t" end="5666340000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle179">但我下意识说了"也不是没有"</p>
<p begin="5666340000t" end="5699700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle180">这样反而让警方更怀疑了</p>
<p begin="5699710000t" end="5723060000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle181">就算如此你还是清白的啊</p>
<p begin="5723070000t" end="5746830000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle182">一定能洗清嫌疑的吧</p>
<p begin="5746840000t" end="5758090000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle183">然而</p>
<p begin="5758110000t" end="5790650000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle184">那个监视器影像让我更不利了</p>
<p begin="5796350000t" end="5825390000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle185">不管说什么都只会被怀疑</p>
<p begin="5846020000t" end="5880290000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle186">你前妻跟我有那么像吗</p>
<p begin="5880300000t" end="5901150000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle187">站在一起的话看得出差别</p>
<p begin="5901160000t" end="5914080000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle188">但还是有点相似</p>
<p begin="5935770000t" end="5972460000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle189">你怎么会跟和我相像的女人结婚呢</p>
<p begin="5979820000t" end="5991660000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle190">是为什么呢</p>
<p begin="6025620000t" end="6050890000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle191">也许是因为我仍忘不了</p>
<p begin="6050900000t" end="6077980000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle192">那天埋在雪里时抬头看见的景象吧</p>
<p begin="6086930000t" end="6112610000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle193">我临死前所见的雪白模样</p>
<p begin="6112630000t" end="6133040000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle194">无论遭遇多少背叛</p>
<p begin="6133060000t" end="6148070000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle195">都不曾褪色</p>
<p begin="6148070000t" end="6168070000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle196">只有那个记忆没有背叛我</p>
<p begin="6197980000t" end="6211870000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle197">糟糕</p>
<p begin="6211880000t" end="6235650000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle198">本来就算撕了嘴也不打算说出口的</p>
<p begin="6240480000t" end="6260240000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle199">但算了 我累得不想再装下去了</p>
<p begin="6265780000t" end="6281950000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle200">这还真是…</p>
<p begin="6293040000t" end="6329080000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle201">那你前妻肯定很不是滋味吧</p>
<p begin="6329080000t" end="6366200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle202">说不定一直有种被拿来跟谁比较的感觉</p>
<p begin="6366200000t" end="6381200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle203">我有在反省</p>
<p begin="6385820000t" end="6407910000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle204">所以知道她外遇时我只觉得这也没办法</p>
<p begin="6407920000t" end="6424460000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle205">离婚时也尽量为她着想</p>
<p begin="6430320000t" end="6452350000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle206">但是不会因为这样就想杀了她吧</p>
<p begin="6463250000t" end="6477850000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle207">我无法提供警察不在场证明</p>
<p begin="6477870000t" end="6506760000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle208">也无法解释一起被拍到的女性是谁</p>
<p begin="6506770000t" end="6527300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle209">结果我的嫌疑就更重了</p>
<p begin="6532390000t" end="6550540000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle210">简直像是踩入陷阱一样</p>
<p begin="6575760000t" end="6597690000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle211">只因为我不能帮你作证</p>
<p begin="6597690000t" end="6625200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle212">就害你的立场变得更艰难了吗</p>
<p begin="6625220000t" end="6645390000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle213">老实说情况非常糟糕</p>
<p begin="6651380000t" end="6677350000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle214">但幸好我有的是钱和时间</p>
<p begin="6677350000t" end="6696950000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle215">我要在变得无法自由行动前</p>
<p begin="6696960000t" end="6721130000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle216">靠自己找出真凶</p>
<p begin="6731130000t" end="6760760000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle217">那样就能证明我是清白的</p>
<p begin="6760760000t" end="6775350000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle218">昌幸…</p>
<p begin="6775370000t" end="6797460000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle219">我没别条路可走了</p>
<p begin="6797480000t" end="6804980000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle220">不…</p>
<p begin="6804990000t" end="6828320000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle221">抱歉 我得离开一段时间</p>
<p begin="6828330000t" end="6852510000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle222">等一下 你有线索吗</p>
<p begin="6852530000t" end="6875460000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle223">总比一直躲在这里好</p>
<p begin="6875470000t" end="6889230000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle224">等一下啦</p>
<p begin="6889230000t" end="6910080000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle225">酒和食物都有库存</p>
<p begin="6910090000t" end="6923840000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle226">我也会留些现金</p>
<p begin="6923840000t" end="6937600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle227">你尽管拿去用</p>
<p begin="6963310000t" end="6980140000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle228">就叫你等一下了</p>
<p begin="6987340000t" end="7016840000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle229">连线索都没有就独自盲目搜索只会失败</p>
<p begin="7016860000t" end="7039370000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle230">警察应该也已经盯着你了</p>
<p begin="7039380000t" end="7054380000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle231">我也会帮你的</p>
<p begin="7054400000t" end="7074820000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle232">别什么都想着一个人来</p>
<p begin="7074840000t" end="7099020000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle233">我知道你是清白的</p>
<p begin="7099030000t" end="7120280000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle234">绝不会眼睁睁看你被抓</p>
<p begin="7139950000t" end="7159900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle235">快喝 快吃吧</p>
<p begin="7159910000t" end="7177840000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle236">是我煎的大阪烧哦</p>
<p begin="7183310000t" end="7194100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle237">没熟…</p>
<p begin="7194120000t" end="7218710000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle238">我想说总比焦掉好…</p>
<p begin="7218730000t" end="7235410000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle239">吃饱就快点睡吧</p>
<p begin="7235420000t" end="7252070000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle240">今晚有美人陪睡哦</p>
<p begin="7274990000t" end="7292960000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle241">听好了 昌幸</p>
<p begin="7292970000t" end="7308390000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle242">你现在先好好休息就是了</p>
<p begin="7318070000t" end="7333410000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle243">讲是这样讲</p>
<p begin="7333420000t" end="7350090000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle244">但今后该如何是好呢</p>
<p begin="7363940000t" end="7387500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle245">她手还是一样那么白呢…</p>
<p begin="7407500000t" end="7416830000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle246">对了</p>
<p begin="7424960000t" end="7454370000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle247">这种时候就要借重公主殿下的力量</p>
<p begin="7454370000t" end="7473510000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle248">那位大人一定会帮助你</p>
<p begin="7473520000t" end="7496070000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle249">也会找出真凶的</p>
<p begin="7496090000t" end="7514850000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle250">那才是真的没问题吗</p>
<p begin="7524900000t" end="7556090000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle251">(九天后)<br />警察并不如预想的频繁前来</p>
<p begin="7562400000t" end="7586150000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle252">在那之后已经超过一个星期了</p>
<p begin="7596130000t" end="7609940000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle253">昌幸</p>
<p begin="7616280000t" end="7635380000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle254">公主殿下亲自过来了</p>
<p begin="7635390000t" end="7647890000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle255">马上去见她吧</p>
<p begin="7647910000t" end="7663750000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle256">要去哪</p>
<p begin="7663750000t" end="7675850000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle257">在深山里</p>
<p begin="7696690000t" end="7708370000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle258">别掉下去咯</p>
<p begin="7795080000t" end="7805560000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle259">公主殿下</p>
<p begin="7841730000t" end="7859340000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle260">这个小女孩就是…</p>
<p begin="7925430000t" end="7952360000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle261">智慧之神的公主殿下?</p>
<p begin="8025900000t" end="8069900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle262">(雪女的不在场证明)</p>
<p begin="8073260000t" end="8085420000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle263">公主殿下</p>
<p begin="8085430000t" end="8128690000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle264">诚心感谢您回应我的请求</p>
<p begin="8128700000t" end="8160910000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle265">那就是我的职责 用不着在意</p>
<p begin="8188090000t" end="8200950000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle266">初次见面你好</p>
<p begin="8200960000t" end="8218040000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle267">我是妖怪 精怪</p>
<p begin="8218060000t" end="8241420000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle268">怪物 怪异 魔物</p>
<p begin="8245950000t" end="8273110000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle269">被这么称呼的存在们的智慧之神</p>
<p begin="8273110000t" end="8294370000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle270">我叫岩永琴子</p>
<p begin="8294380000t" end="8312300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle271">我受到雪女的委托</p>
<p begin="8312310000t" end="8342750000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle272">前来解决这起与你有关的事件</p>
<p begin="8342770000t" end="8359030000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle273">我是室井昌幸</p>
<p begin="8359030000t" end="8377380000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle274">不好意思劳烦您特地来…</p>
<p begin="8377390000t" end="8408650000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle275">虽然直接去你家也可以</p>
<p begin="8408660000t" end="8430760000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle276">但像我这样引人注目的人登门拜访</p>
<p begin="8430770000t" end="8444770000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle277">只怕会给你添麻烦</p>
<p begin="8459410000t" end="8476640000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle278">在这里虽然冷了些</p>
<p begin="8476660000t" end="8498320000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle279">不过说说话还是可以的</p>
<p begin="8498330000t" end="8519180000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle280">您是独自前来的吗</p>
<p begin="8519190000t" end="8552120000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle281">我听说您有恋人 那位…</p>
<p begin="8566530000t" end="8603420000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle282">我当然有邀他一起来</p>
<p begin="8617870000t" end="8651820000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle283">但他说要去工地打工就拒绝了</p>
<p begin="8651820000t" end="8667250000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle284">比起可爱的女朋友</p>
<p begin="8667250000t" end="8692270000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle285">居然优先选择深夜的隧道工程</p>
<p begin="8692290000t" end="8729400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle286">我也知道研究所学生很需要钱</p>
<p begin="8729410000t" end="8749520000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle287">但我都说了那点钱我家可以出</p>
<p begin="8749530000t" end="8761500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle288">他却根本不理我</p>
<p begin="8761520000t" end="8800720000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle289">害我只能在附近的便利商店买便当跟饮料</p>
<p begin="8800720000t" end="8834230000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle290">让怪物们送我到这深山里来</p>
<p begin="8838400000t" end="8859000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle291">以前明明为我准备过亲手做的便当</p>
<p begin="8858990000t" end="8882790000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle292">跟热腾腾的猪肉味噌汤</p>
<p begin="8882790000t" end="8902210000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle293">真不晓得那男人怎么好意思</p>
<p begin="8902200000t" end="8931200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle294">让我落到只能吃冷冰冰的炸猪排的地步</p>
<p begin="8944320000t" end="8967540000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle295">不好意思 说太多闲话了</p>
<p begin="8967550000t" end="9000910000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle296">一直为这种事发脾气也不是办法</p>
<p begin="9000920000t" end="9047210000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle297">我事前确认过你们的状况和事件概要</p>
<p begin="9047220000t" end="9068040000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle298">没想到因为证人是雪女</p>
<p begin="9068060000t" end="9084330000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle299">反而加深了你的嫌疑</p>
<p begin="9084340000t" end="9111860000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle300">或许可说是人类与妖怪随意扯上关系</p>
<p begin="9111870000t" end="9143980000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle301">很容易引来不可预测的危险的好例子呢</p>
<p begin="9143990000t" end="9163990000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle302">这个男人明明是无辜的</p>
<p begin="9164000000t" end="9191930000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle303">却因为我陷入艰难的立场</p>
<p begin="9191950000t" end="9231150000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle304">虽然他长得很凶恶 但绝不是坏人</p>
<p begin="9231150000t" end="9246150000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle305">还请您务必伸出援手</p>
<p begin="9246160000t" end="9264510000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle306">不是你的错</p>
<p begin="9264520000t" end="9280860000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle307">对吧 室井先生</p>
<p begin="9285090000t" end="9314140000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle308">是我自己不好 她没有错</p>
<p begin="9314160000t" end="9324160000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle309">话虽如此</p>
<p begin="9324160000t" end="9360860000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle310">这种状况实在凑巧得太让人不愉快了</p>
<p begin="9360860000t" end="9382970000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle311">无论是只有雪女能作证的不在场证明</p>
<p begin="9382980000t" end="9418840000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle312">还是被错认为前妻的监视器影像</p>
<p begin="9418840000t" end="9441770000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle313">这些让你被逼入绝境的要素</p>
<p begin="9441780000t" end="9466380000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle314">反而会让人觉得是准备周到的设定</p>
<p begin="9466390000t" end="9499750000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle315">那么 这部分不就会让人起疑了吗</p>
<p begin="9514800000t" end="9574400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle316">承认妖怪存在真的就能证明你的不在场证明是真的吗</p>
<p begin="9574420000t" end="9596100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle317">妖怪与人的寿命相异</p>
<p begin="9596100000t" end="9616530000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle318">对时间流逝的感觉也不一样</p>
<p begin="9616530000t" end="9639050000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle319">它们根本不会使用月历之类的东西</p>
<p begin="9638990000t" end="9685090000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle320">也不见得能跟人类一样正确掌握今天是什么日期</p>
<p begin="9689700000t" end="9706200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle321">那么雪女我问你</p>
<p begin="9706210000t" end="9742490000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle322">你有办法正确说出今天是几月几日吗</p>
<p begin="9760530000t" end="9797120000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle323">那个…我只知道是十月初</p>
<p begin="9813790000t" end="9857100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle324">只要室井先生说事件发生的12日就是那天的那个时候</p>
<p begin="9857200000t" end="9893470000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle325">雪女就会觉得"你是说那一天啊"</p>
<p begin="9893490000t" end="9930590000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle326">即使实际上是11日或13日</p>
<p begin="9930610000t" end="9951040000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle327">你都无法正确分辨</p>
<p begin="9951050000t" end="9984400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle328">只要室井先生有心让你记错日期</p>
<p begin="9984410000t" end="10001070000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle329">你马上就会上当</p>
<p begin="10008070000t" end="10045710000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle330">也就是说他还是有可能在12日杀害前妻</p>
<p begin="10057830000t" end="10071570000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle331">你的不在场证明…</p>
<p begin="10071580000t" end="10099510000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle332">就算承认雪女当证人也是不成立的</p>
<p begin="10105620000t" end="10123280000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle333">监视器影像也一样</p>
<p begin="10123300000t" end="10149980000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle334">只要事前调查美春小姐的日常行动</p>
<p begin="10149990000t" end="10183760000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle335">就能在无法确认她人在何处的时候</p>
<p begin="10183780000t" end="10224480000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle336">带着雪女一起被监视器拍到</p>
<p begin="10230190000t" end="10257590000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle337">你也无法证明你们真的是碰巧被拍到的吧</p>
<p begin="10257590000t" end="10281780000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle338">你敢说你特殊的不在场证明和影像</p>
<p begin="10281790000t" end="10302620000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle339">都不是伪造的吗</p>
<p begin="10308340000t" end="10328460000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle340">我那么做有什么意义</p>
<p begin="10333200000t" end="10351840000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle341">你说得好像我伪造不在场证明</p>
<p begin="10351850000t" end="10376450000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle342">还故意被监视器拍到</p>
<p begin="10376460000t" end="10400210000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle343">但这些只会陷我于不利</p>
<p begin="10400220000t" end="10409810000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle344">根本得不到好处</p>
<p begin="10415640000t" end="10439020000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle345">这样下去我会被警察逮捕</p>
<p begin="10439030000t" end="10459880000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle346">也没有方法证明我的清白</p>
<p begin="10459890000t" end="10477070000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle347">是有好处的哦</p>
<p begin="10480590000t" end="10513000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle348">那就是雪女对你绝不动摇的信赖</p>
<p begin="10517500000t" end="10527020000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle349">什么</p>
<p begin="10527030000t" end="10573740000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle350">雪女一旦相信你的清白便不会再怀疑</p>
<p begin="10573750000t" end="10607110000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle351">之后无论用任何手段都会想帮助你</p>
<p begin="10607110000t" end="10638460000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle352">满脑子都只想要帮你吧</p>
<p begin="10653270000t" end="10686340000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle353">意识到自己害你更不利</p>
<p begin="10686350000t" end="10715960000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle354">便会因为罪恶感完全成为你的同伴</p>
<p begin="10723930000t" end="10757240000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle355">你有好几个有充足理由报仇的对象</p>
<p begin="10763250000t" end="10796050000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle356">想杀掉你的朋友 前妻</p>
<p begin="10796050000t" end="10824320000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle357">背叛你夺走公司的伙伴们</p>
<p begin="10828820000t" end="10847760000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle358">虽然前两位已经死了</p>
<p begin="10847770000t" end="10862780000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle359">但其他人还活着对吧</p>
<p begin="10867000000t" end="10895100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle360">既然做得到解除你的职位并夺权</p>
<p begin="10895110000t" end="10914500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle361">应该不只两三个人</p>
<p begin="10914510000t" end="10945770000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle362">要杀掉所有人还平安无事是挺困难的</p>
<p begin="10953660000t" end="10988780000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle363">但如果获得雪女帮助就不一样了</p>
<p begin="10992960000t" end="11015420000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle364">因为美春小姐的事件被抓的你</p>
<p begin="11015390000t" end="11052890000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle365">只要对雪女说"我发现是以前的同伴害怕被追究贪污"</p>
<p begin="11052970000t" end="11075480000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle366">"才陷害我的"</p>
<p begin="11075490000t" end="11099260000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle367">"我无力证明自己的清白"</p>
<p begin="11099280000t" end="11116360000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle368">"也没办法追究他们贪污"</p>
<p begin="11116370000t" end="11148060000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle369">"拜托你替我向他们报仇"</p>
<p begin="11148070000t" end="11168920000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle370">如果你这样恳切地拜托她</p>
<p begin="11168930000t" end="11208540000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle371">相信你清白的雪女就会照做吧</p>
<p begin="11213070000t" end="11245250000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle372">妖怪并不受人类的法律和伦理约束</p>
<p begin="11245260000t" end="11286820000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle373">雪女会相信你的说词而把那些人冻死吧</p>
<p begin="11354000000t" end="11378710000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle374">她是在害怕公主殿下的假设吗</p>
<p begin="11395360000t" end="11431250000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle375">她明明这么依赖公主殿下…</p>
<p begin="11450320000t" end="11474320000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle376">让自己身处安全之处达成复仇</p>
<p begin="11478320000t" end="11497150000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle377">为了达成这个最终目的</p>
<p begin="11497170000t" end="11524260000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle378">你计划杀害美春小姐</p>
<p begin="11524280000t" end="11551370000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle379">并故意营造自己受到怀疑的状况</p>
<p begin="11551380000t" end="11572230000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle380">好利用雪女</p>
<p begin="11572240000t" end="11586410000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle381">我有说错吗</p>
<p begin="11602300000t" end="11641460000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle382">虽然我打从一开始就不期待这个智慧之神</p>
<p begin="11641470000t" end="11673580000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle383">但没想到她竟然说得出这么荒诞的言论</p>
<p begin="11685150000t" end="11709450000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle384">这假设根本站不住脚</p>
<p begin="11709460000t" end="11726550000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle385">就算真的靠这样达成复仇好了</p>
<p begin="11726560000t" end="11765350000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle386">之后因为杀死美春被判刑的话就没意义了吧</p>
<p begin="11765360000t" end="11795380000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle387">你可是有雪女这妖怪的帮助哦</p>
<p begin="11795380000t" end="11812050000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle388">等达成复仇后</p>
<p begin="11812070000t" end="11833750000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle389">告诉她 你想到脱身的方法</p>
<p begin="11833750000t" end="11862520000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle390">指使她做新的行动就行了</p>
<p begin="11862520000t" end="11898390000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle391">让她去购物中心给监视器拍</p>
<p begin="11898400000t" end="11932590000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle392">再委托律师去调查影像</p>
<p begin="11932600000t" end="11951360000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle393">只要证明美春小姐过世后</p>
<p begin="11951370000t" end="11985150000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle394">那位与她相像的女性仍有出入</p>
<p begin="11985160000t" end="12011600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle395">就能推翻警察怀疑你的根据</p>
<p begin="12016470000t" end="12041450000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle396">就算检方掌握什么有力证据</p>
<p begin="12041450000t" end="12064800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle397">也可以叫雪女在开庭前去偷出来</p>
<p begin="12064810000t" end="12081070000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle398">找地方藏起来</p>
<p begin="12081080000t" end="12114440000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle399">想要获得无罪或不起诉的判决也并非难事</p>
<p begin="12123830000t" end="12147400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle400">只是与妖怪有点小交易的话</p>
<p begin="12147400000t" end="12161990000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle401">我可以睁一只眼闭一只眼</p>
<p begin="12162000000t" end="12214540000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle402">但我不可能放过为了私欲操控妖怪的人</p>
<p begin="12218690000t" end="12256250000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle403">这可是会颠覆人类妖怪两界秩序的行为</p>
<p begin="12273440000t" end="12284200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle404">公主殿下</p>
<p begin="12305190000t" end="12319230000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle405">虽然您这么说</p>
<p begin="12319230000t" end="12351340000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle406">但这个男人不可能想出那么邪恶的计划</p>
<p begin="12372190000t" end="12384710000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle407">我的确…</p>
<p begin="12384720000t" end="12422240000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle408">我的确深信这个男人的清白</p>
<p begin="12422260000t" end="12461450000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle409">应该也能毫不犹豫地为了他杀人</p>
<p begin="12468400000t" end="12517340000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle410">我并非怀疑公主殿下的智慧与慧眼</p>
<p begin="12517360000t" end="12549040000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle411">但是这男人面恶心善</p>
<p begin="12549050000t" end="12577400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle412">根本无法憎恨其他人</p>
<p begin="12577410000t" end="12612860000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle413">要不然怎么会多次被人背叛 伤害</p>
<p begin="12612870000t" end="12638710000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle414">变得无法相信他人呢</p>
<p begin="12652590000t" end="12662660000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle415">还请您…</p>
<p begin="12667330000t" end="12685850000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle416">请您务必重新考虑</p>
<p begin="12822380000t" end="12838920000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle417">我知道啦</p>
<p begin="12838930000t" end="12867280000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle418">我很清楚室井先生不是犯人</p>
<p begin="12867290000t" end="12888140000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle419">刚才说的全都是假的哦</p>
<p begin="12940540000t" end="12951940000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle420">你说什么</p>
<p begin="12951950000t" end="12986990000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle421">虽然我的假设里也有几个问题</p>
<p begin="12990670000t" end="13018260000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle422">不过如果你真的想骗取雪女信赖的话</p>
<p begin="13018270000t" end="13048690000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle423">应该早就跟她上床了吧</p>
<p begin="13052870000t" end="13071630000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle424">毕竟有了肉体关系</p>
<p begin="13071630000t" end="13096250000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle425">更能确实让她对你深信不疑</p>
<p begin="13096260000t" end="13107920000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle426">这品性…</p>
<p begin="13111300000t" end="13159650000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle427">听说雪女引诱你好几次了都没成功</p>
<p begin="13159670000t" end="13186340000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle428">我还想说这哪来的软脚虾啊</p>
<p begin="13186350000t" end="13232650000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle429">这种人是不可能想出并执行我说的计划的</p>
<p begin="13232660000t" end="13261420000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle430">所以我的假设根本不成立</p>
<p begin="13276800000t" end="13306050000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle431">那你为什么要撒这些谎</p>
<p begin="13306050000t" end="13328980000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle432">只是为了捉弄我们的话也太恶劣了吧</p>
<p begin="13329000000t" end="13348550000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle433">是为了告诉你哦</p>
<p begin="13356040000t" end="13376530000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle434">雪女为了庇护你</p>
<p begin="13376540000t" end="13412400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle435">甚至不惜试图反驳身为神的我</p>
<p begin="13412410000t" end="13436600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle436">你知道这需要多少勇气吗</p>
<p begin="13436610000t" end="13469970000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle437">她为了你连神都反抗了哦</p>
<p begin="13494430000t" end="13508340000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle438">尽管她是妖怪</p>
<p begin="13508350000t" end="13541710000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle439">仍然信任你并真心为你付出</p>
<p begin="13541720000t" end="13555880000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle440">你至今受了很多伤</p>
<p begin="13555890000t" end="13583830000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle441">或许非常害怕再去相信人</p>
<p begin="13583840000t" end="13603840000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle442">但你身边有这样支持你的对象</p>
<p begin="13610660000t" end="13631370000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle443">也差不多该振作起来了吧</p>
<p begin="13658550000t" end="13675890000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle444">我在做什么啊</p>
<p begin="13682120000t" end="13695600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle445">我的确是因为受了伤</p>
<p begin="13695610000t" end="13712290000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle446">对生活感到厌倦才逃来这里的</p>
<p begin="13712300000t" end="13743980000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle447">再度见到雪女后也获得一丝平静</p>
<p begin="13744000000t" end="13773590000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle448">但还是觉得有些内疚</p>
<p begin="13773610000t" end="13805710000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle449">害怕再跟人扯上关系 变得胆小</p>
<p begin="13805730000t" end="13822810000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle450">无法拿出勇气</p>
<p begin="13832820000t" end="13856180000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle451">虽然你下场如何不关我的事</p>
<p begin="13856190000t" end="13902480000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle452">但我作为智慧之神必须完成雪女的委托</p>
<p begin="13902490000t" end="13926250000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle453">只是解决事件的话</p>
<p begin="13926260000t" end="13950860000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle454">还称不上是帮了你吧</p>
<p begin="13950860000t" end="13972530000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle455">抱歉 的确如此</p>
<p begin="14007180000t" end="14020930000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle456">抱歉给你添麻烦了</p>
<p begin="14082400000t" end="14113530000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle457">那么美春的杀人事件该怎么办</p>
<p begin="14117750000t" end="14139390000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle458">没逮到真凶的话</p>
<p begin="14139400000t" end="14163160000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle459">我的状况还是很危险</p>
<p begin="14169410000t" end="14188590000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle460">我知道真凶是谁</p>
<p begin="14201560000t" end="14225300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle461">虽然不是什么需要着急的问题</p>
<p begin="14225310000t" end="14261590000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle462">不过我就顺便说说这部分该怎么解决吧</p>
<p begin="14270090000t" end="14299800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle463">(待续)</p>
